1
00:00:27,530 --> 00:00:38,530
Koncom 19. storočia sa vo Vietname 
stala 14-ročná May treťou manželkou bohatého statkára. 
(Príbeh je inšpirovaný skutočnými udalosťami)

2
00:00:38,530 --> 00:00:44,530
Tretia manželka

3
00:08:55,530 --> 00:08:56,660
Moje vnučky.

4
00:08:56,990 --> 00:08:58,580
Poďte ku mne.

5
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,830
Moje pekné dievčatká.

6
00:09:05,290 --> 00:09:06,830
Vy dve.

7
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:09,460
Videli ste nové teliatko?

8
00:09:09,460 --> 00:09:10,590
Ešte nie.

9
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:13,510
Nesledovali pôrod.

10
00:09:13,550 --> 00:09:17,010
Zajtra im to teľa ukážem.

11
00:09:19,560 --> 00:09:21,850
Teľa nemá veľkú cenu.

12
00:09:23,810 --> 00:09:24,810
No ak ho predáme,

13
00:09:24,810 --> 00:09:27,940
môžeme dievčatám kúpiť nový odev?

14
00:09:29,940 --> 00:09:31,320
Ja viem,

15
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:34,900
že by chcel Son nového koňa.

16
00:09:36,410 --> 00:09:38,120
To je pravda.

17
00:09:48,460 --> 00:09:50,000
Otec.

18
00:09:50,250 --> 00:09:53,050
Môj syn má vek na ženenie.

19
00:09:54,260 --> 00:09:57,300
Mali by sme na to šetriť.

20
00:09:57,590 --> 00:09:59,600
Máš pravdu.

21
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:02,890
Dostane teda brat Son nového koňa?

22
00:10:02,930 --> 00:10:05,520
Môžem ho dostať aj ja?

23
00:10:05,810 --> 00:10:07,520
Mama?

24
00:10:08,350 --> 00:10:10,020
Moja drahá.

25
00:10:23,990 --> 00:10:25,660
Len pi.

26
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:29,000
Hľuza, lotosové semienka a palina.

27
00:10:29,170 --> 00:10:31,630
Sú dobré pre tvoju krv.

28
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:39,220
Nhan, jedz!

29
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:43,310
Chutí?

30
00:10:46,310 --> 00:10:47,980
Dedinský lekár

31
00:10:48,060 --> 00:10:50,770
to robieval pani Ha.

32
00:10:50,980 --> 00:10:52,610
Keď čakala pána Sona,

33
00:10:52,650 --> 00:10:54,610
neustále som sa s pani Ha modlila.

34
00:10:54,610 --> 00:10:56,150
Keď sa narodil,

35
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:57,320
mal silné nohy a ruky.

36
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,860
Silný plač.

37
00:10:58,860 --> 00:11:00,860
Mala som radosť.

38
00:11:02,780 --> 00:11:04,700
Chcem chlapca.

39
00:11:04,950 --> 00:11:06,700
Správne.

40
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:12,710
Pani Xuan ešte nie je skutočnou 
paňou domácnosti.

41
00:11:12,710 --> 00:11:16,880
Pretože pánovi Hungovi ešte neporodila syna.

42
00:11:39,610 --> 00:11:41,570
Je to presne uprostred.

43
00:11:41,660 --> 00:11:43,360
Je to na vrchole.

44
00:11:43,370 --> 00:11:44,910
Ten je ukrytý.

45
00:11:44,910 --> 00:11:47,580
Ak sa chceš dostať k vrcholu, 
musíš byť trpezlivá.

46
00:11:48,330 --> 00:11:51,710
Musíš s tým počkať naňho.

47
00:11:51,790 --> 00:11:54,170
Ako vieš, kedy sa to stane?

48
00:11:54,290 --> 00:11:56,170
To zistíš.

49
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,590
Každá žena je iná.

50
00:11:58,630 --> 00:11:59,880
Pravda.

51
00:12:00,260 --> 00:12:03,840
Ja to viem, keď začnem cítiť teplo v nohách.

52
00:12:04,180 --> 00:12:06,470
Mysli na to ako na tanec.

53
00:12:08,180 --> 00:12:09,930
Najskôr si to spravíš sama.

54
00:12:10,180 --> 00:12:12,770
Naučíš sa, aké je tvoje telo.

55
00:12:12,890 --> 00:12:14,810
Keď si potom s ním,

56
00:12:14,860 --> 00:12:17,770
ukážeš mu, čo si pamätáš.

57
00:12:18,530 --> 00:12:19,780
Takto.

58
00:12:33,620 --> 00:12:34,620
Tu.

59
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:43,430
Keď do mňa prenikne, cítim len bolesť.

60
00:12:43,470 --> 00:12:44,970
Tvár sa, že sa ti to páči.

61
00:12:44,970 --> 00:12:46,890
Aby sa mu to páčilo.

62
00:12:47,180 --> 00:12:49,640
Jedného dňa sa ti to zapáči tiež.

63
00:12:51,640 --> 00:12:55,390
Sestra Ha to cíti, len keď je manžel drsný.

64
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,400
Drsný?

65
00:12:58,270 --> 00:13:02,940
Len sa smejte, kým nie ste na rade.

66
00:13:04,990 --> 00:13:08,370
To s tebou spraví pôrod.

67
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,000
Tu.

68
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:17,880
Skús to.

69
00:13:19,420 --> 00:13:21,130
Pekné.

70
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,520
Poď dnu.

71
00:13:41,530 --> 00:13:43,530
Áno, pani.

72
00:14:32,950 --> 00:14:35,290
Na kolená.

73
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:44,420
Nie na posteli.

74
00:14:46,460 --> 00:14:48,090
Na zemi.

75
00:15:04,730 --> 00:15:06,110
Plaz sa ku mne.

76
00:15:15,490 --> 00:15:17,080
Poď sem.

77
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:07,750
Daj si lepkavú ryžu.

78
00:16:18,970 --> 00:16:19,930
Lien.

79
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:22,190
Krvácaš.

80
00:16:25,770 --> 00:16:26,690
Tu.

81
00:16:26,900 --> 00:16:28,190
Ďakujem.

82
00:16:29,530 --> 00:16:32,450
Mama! Lien krváca!

83
00:16:37,740 --> 00:16:40,870
Mama, konečne.

84
00:16:48,130 --> 00:16:50,960
- Obleč si tieto.
- Teta Lao, Lien krváca!

85
00:17:12,190 --> 00:17:14,070
Tie žlté kvietky sa ti nepáčia?

86
00:17:14,150 --> 00:17:15,110
Nie, pani.

87
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:16,990
Teta Lao povedala, že je to ľulok.

88
00:17:16,990 --> 00:17:17,820
Je veľmi jedovatý.

89
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:19,120
Ponáhľajte sa!

90
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:20,540
Prší!

91
00:17:20,580 --> 00:17:22,540
Áno, mama!

92
00:19:33,380 --> 00:19:34,880
Zase?

93
00:19:54,940 --> 00:19:56,900
Lien! Pozri!

94
00:19:56,980 --> 00:19:57,980
Lien!

95
00:19:59,070 --> 00:20:00,900
To nie!

96
00:20:06,990 --> 00:20:09,120
Nechajte to, deti!

97
00:20:12,460 --> 00:20:14,250
Uprace to sluha.

98
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:16,590
Poďte.

99
00:20:29,390 --> 00:20:31,430
Tu máte čaj.

100
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:49,990
Rozumiem...

101
00:20:50,830 --> 00:20:52,910
prečo ťa má môj syn

102
00:20:53,410 --> 00:20:57,500
teraz najradšej.

103
00:20:59,670 --> 00:21:01,130
Otec.

104
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:05,890
Nechaj nás.

105
00:21:07,600 --> 00:21:09,310
Choď von.

106
00:21:09,510 --> 00:21:11,470
Otec, pani.

107
00:21:33,250 --> 00:21:34,660
Otec.

108
00:21:36,750 --> 00:21:39,290
Nepustite si ju priveľmi k telu.

109
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:46,090
Nemusíš sa báť.

110
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:51,430
To dieťa nie je Wu Zetian.

111
00:21:58,900 --> 00:22:00,650
Napokon...

112
00:22:00,980 --> 00:22:02,980
nie sme nič viac, než prach...

113
00:22:03,070 --> 00:22:05,740
v Budhovom tieni.

114
00:22:19,330 --> 00:22:20,500
May.

115
00:22:23,710 --> 00:22:24,960
Počúvaj.

116
00:22:25,210 --> 00:22:27,550
Nespoliehaj sa na svoje dieťa.

117
00:22:28,380 --> 00:22:30,510
Lien sa čoskoro vydá.

118
00:22:31,510 --> 00:22:32,680
Aj z nej bude

119
00:22:32,720 --> 00:22:35,180
skutočná dáma.

120
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:37,730
Nie je tvoja slúžka.

121
00:22:38,520 --> 00:22:39,980
Rozumela si?

122
00:22:39,980 --> 00:22:41,440
Áno, pani.

123
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:55,430
Lien!

124
00:23:55,760 --> 00:23:56,720
Bež spať!

125
00:23:56,810 --> 00:24:00,480
Keď vyrastiem, bude zo mňa muž.

126
00:24:01,270 --> 00:24:02,060
Naozaj!

127
00:24:02,060 --> 00:24:03,270
Nhan!

128
00:24:03,310 --> 00:24:06,820
Budem muž a budem mať veľa žien.

129
00:24:06,980 --> 00:24:08,400
Modlím sa za to k Budhovi.

130
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:10,240
Stane sa to!

131
00:32:23,770 --> 00:32:26,270
Prečo ich trestať? Prečo ich nevyženú?

132
00:32:26,320 --> 00:32:28,860
Otehotnela mimo sobáš.

133
00:32:28,860 --> 00:32:30,860
Nemôžeme ich nechať ísť.

134
00:32:35,320 --> 00:32:37,790
Čo sa stane jej a dieťaťu, ktoré nosí?

135
00:32:38,370 --> 00:32:41,580
Ona a jej dieťa teraz patria chrámu.

136
00:32:42,080 --> 00:32:44,040
A čo on?

137
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:45,580
On bude potrestaný najviac,

138
00:32:45,630 --> 00:32:47,590
ale o prácu nepríde.

139
00:34:27,350 --> 00:34:28,690
Teta Lao.

140
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:32,150
Kde je klobúk na zakrytie?

141
00:34:34,820 --> 00:34:35,820
Pani.

142
00:34:42,330 --> 00:34:43,450
Zvládnete to?

143
00:34:43,450 --> 00:34:45,370
Áno, ďakujem.

144
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:50,540
Nhan, Lien.

145
00:34:50,580 --> 00:34:51,710
Poďte sem.

146
00:34:52,170 --> 00:34:54,000
Áno, teta.

147
00:34:59,680 --> 00:35:01,600
Vonia to dobre.

148
00:36:41,780 --> 00:36:42,780
May.

149
00:36:42,990 --> 00:36:44,360
Nejedz to.

150
00:36:44,410 --> 00:36:45,870
Guava je zlá pre dieťa.

151
00:36:45,910 --> 00:36:47,580
Dobre.

152
00:37:17,980 --> 00:37:19,360
Drž.

153
00:37:29,660 --> 00:37:30,990
Nôž.

154
00:37:34,410 --> 00:37:35,960
Tanier.

155
00:37:57,230 --> 00:37:57,850
Drž to tam.

156
00:37:57,850 --> 00:37:58,810
Drž to takto.

157
00:37:58,820 --> 00:38:00,820
Áno, pani.

158
00:38:28,550 --> 00:38:31,140
Mama, pozri.

159
00:38:31,430 --> 00:38:32,600
Vyber ich.

160
00:38:32,640 --> 00:38:34,430
- Stôl je plný jedla.
- Áno, mama.

161
00:38:35,180 --> 00:38:36,480
Tu.

162
00:38:36,940 --> 00:38:38,390
Sestra Ha dnes zapáli kadidlo.

163
00:38:38,400 --> 00:38:40,690
Ty si tehotná a ja krvácam.

164
00:38:40,690 --> 00:38:42,150
Teta Lao.

165
00:38:42,190 --> 00:38:43,900
Áno.

166
00:38:44,030 --> 00:38:45,030
Pani?

167
00:38:45,070 --> 00:38:48,110
Zavoláte pani Ha?
 Sme pripravené na odchod.

168
00:38:49,700 --> 00:38:53,080
Pani Ha dnes kadidlo zapáliť nemôže.

169
00:38:53,120 --> 00:38:54,700
Nechajte to na mne.

170
00:38:54,790 --> 00:38:56,080
Tu.

171
00:38:57,460 --> 00:38:59,080
Nemôže?

172
00:39:33,700 --> 00:39:35,040
Sestra.

173
00:39:35,120 --> 00:39:36,750
Blahoželám.

174
00:39:38,370 --> 00:39:40,170
Ďakujem.

175
00:39:40,330 --> 00:39:42,000
Nech je požehnané.

176
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:44,000
Nhan, Lien poďte!

177
00:39:47,340 --> 00:39:49,630
Položte to na oltár.

178
00:40:06,730 --> 00:40:08,780
Prosím, vypočuj moje modlitby.

179
00:40:08,990 --> 00:40:11,030
Prosím, daj mi syna.

180
00:40:12,490 --> 00:40:15,780
Dovoľ, nech som jediná, ktorá porodí syna.

181
00:41:14,840 --> 00:41:17,260
Kedy sa vydáš?

182
00:41:18,220 --> 00:41:20,020
Neviem.

183
00:41:20,140 --> 00:41:23,020
Pani Ha vraví, že po Sonovej svadbe.

184
00:41:23,230 --> 00:41:25,770
Prídeš sa so mnou potom ešte hrať?

185
00:41:25,770 --> 00:41:29,320
Už sa môžeš hrať s Dove!

186
00:41:29,940 --> 00:41:32,530
Kto bude tvoj manžel?

187
00:41:32,690 --> 00:41:34,400
To zatiaľ neviem.

188
00:41:35,240 --> 00:41:37,280
Koľká budeš manželka?

189
00:41:37,370 --> 00:41:39,700
Prvá, samozrejme. Ktorá iná by som bola?

190
00:41:39,740 --> 00:41:42,120
Ako vieš, že budeš prvá?

191
00:41:42,160 --> 00:41:45,170
Viem to. Sľúbila mi to pani Ha.

192
00:41:45,290 --> 00:41:47,000
Budem prvá manželka.

193
00:41:47,040 --> 00:41:48,710
Však, pani?

194
00:41:49,790 --> 00:41:53,510
Budem ti chýbať, keď sa vydáš?

195
00:41:53,550 --> 00:41:55,510
Áno.

196
00:42:16,910 --> 00:42:18,490
Neožením sa!

197
00:42:18,530 --> 00:42:19,320
Son!

198
00:42:19,450 --> 00:42:21,490
Nepribližuj sa!

199
00:42:21,620 --> 00:42:23,500
Zmizni!

200
00:42:24,200 --> 00:42:26,000
Nechaj ma na pokoji!

201
00:42:26,370 --> 00:42:28,120
To sa radšej zabijem!

202
00:42:28,120 --> 00:42:29,170
Son!

203
00:42:30,500 --> 00:42:32,000
Zbláznil si sa?

204
00:42:51,150 --> 00:42:53,280
Matka...

205
00:42:57,150 --> 00:43:01,660
Nemôžem sa oženiť s ženou, ktorú nepoznám.

206
00:43:06,080 --> 00:43:09,580
Ani ja som tvojho otca nepoznala.

207
00:43:14,920 --> 00:43:18,340
Prvý raz sme sa stretli vo svadobný deň.

208
00:43:45,120 --> 00:43:46,910
Uhorka, preber sa.

209
00:43:47,160 --> 00:43:48,410
Zobuď sa, prosím.

210
00:43:48,460 --> 00:43:51,120
Nechaj ho. Čoskoro umrie.

211
00:43:51,170 --> 00:43:53,130
To nehovor!

212
00:43:53,750 --> 00:43:55,960
Uhorka, preber sa!

213
00:43:56,170 --> 00:43:58,010
Vstaň, prosím.

214
00:44:02,760 --> 00:44:05,390
Uhorka!

215
00:44:05,470 --> 00:44:06,510
Pusti ma!

216
00:44:06,510 --> 00:44:07,390
Nie!

217
00:44:07,520 --> 00:44:10,390
Pusti ma!

218
00:44:10,440 --> 00:44:11,440
Nhan!

219
00:44:11,440 --> 00:44:13,730
Nejedz to!

220
00:44:13,770 --> 00:44:15,440
Nie!

221
00:44:22,490 --> 00:44:25,990
Prečo ho kŕmiš ľulokom?

222
00:44:26,330 --> 00:44:29,450
Leží už celé týždne.

223
00:44:30,370 --> 00:44:33,120
Je načase nechať ho ísť.

224
00:44:35,750 --> 00:44:39,260
Nenechám ho umrieť v deň Sonovej svadby.

225
00:44:54,480 --> 00:44:56,270
Otvor ústa.

226
00:44:58,860 --> 00:45:00,150
Otvor!

227
00:45:02,700 --> 00:45:03,610
Nhan!

228
00:45:03,820 --> 00:45:05,740
Počuješ ma?

229
00:45:06,870 --> 00:45:08,410
Chceš tu zostať celú noc?

230
00:45:08,410 --> 00:45:09,410
Otvor!

231
00:45:09,450 --> 00:45:11,330
Už aj!

232
00:46:38,580 --> 00:46:40,380
Xuan!

233
00:46:40,710 --> 00:46:41,880
Nechaj ma tak!

234
00:46:41,960 --> 00:46:43,380
Zase si pil?

235
00:46:43,460 --> 00:46:45,510
Naozaj to chceš?

236
00:46:45,590 --> 00:46:47,680
Chcem normálny život.

237
00:46:47,970 --> 00:46:50,010
Na tomto nie je nič normálne.

238
00:46:50,090 --> 00:46:52,430
Máme spolu dieťa.

239
00:46:55,770 --> 00:46:57,770
Ona nie je tvoja.

240
00:46:57,810 --> 00:47:00,860
Jej otec je aj tvoj otec.

241
00:47:01,690 --> 00:47:03,150
Čo?

242
00:47:03,230 --> 00:47:05,280
Klameš!

243
00:47:13,830 --> 00:47:16,200
Nie je to tvoje dieťa.

244
00:47:16,450 --> 00:47:21,920
Vývar z bodliakov zo mňa 
vyplavil všetko tvoje semeno.

245
00:47:23,420 --> 00:47:26,550
Neklam sám seba.

246
00:47:29,430 --> 00:47:31,260
Prosím, odíď.

247
00:47:33,760 --> 00:47:35,890
Ty...

248
00:47:37,310 --> 00:47:40,230
Milovala si ma niekedy?

249
00:48:43,370 --> 00:48:46,250
Veľmi ju milujem.

250
00:48:46,540 --> 00:48:47,840
Rozumiem,

251
00:48:47,880 --> 00:48:49,550
ale tak to byť nemôže.

252
00:48:49,880 --> 00:48:51,630
Ako tomu môžeš rozumieť?

253
00:48:51,720 --> 00:48:54,470
Nikdy si nikoho nemilovala.

254
00:48:58,810 --> 00:49:01,100
Niekoho áno.

255
00:49:03,390 --> 00:49:05,690
Než som sem prišla,

256
00:49:07,230 --> 00:49:12,280
zasľúbila som sa mužovi.

257
00:49:13,780 --> 00:49:15,530
Bol to rybár.

258
00:49:17,780 --> 00:49:20,160
Dal mi tento kameň.

259
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:23,330
Našiel ho na dne rieky,

260
00:49:23,330 --> 00:49:26,040
ktorá tiekla vedľa našej dediny.

261
00:49:28,380 --> 00:49:29,920
Čo sa stalo?

262
00:49:32,050 --> 00:49:34,800
Už je to dávno.

263
00:49:52,780 --> 00:49:54,490
Spi.

264
00:50:13,050 --> 00:50:14,590
Lien.

