328
01:02:44,340 --> 01:02:46,340
Ty ma nemiluješ.

329
01:02:48,140 --> 01:02:50,550
Milujem.

330
01:02:55,230 --> 01:02:56,980
Ale...

331
01:02:59,900 --> 01:03:02,730
si mi ako dcéra.

332
01:03:57,200 --> 01:03:58,830
Tvojej dcéry,

333
01:03:58,830 --> 01:04:00,500
